site_name: Development At Hainault House And Land On The South Side Of
description: Site B of the wider Billet Road opportunity site - Redevelopment of site for residential / mix use to provide 539no. residential dwellings comprising of single dwelling houses and blocks of flats of up to five storeys (mixture of 1, 2, 3 and 4 bedrooms) and commercial / community floorspace with associated bicycle and refuse stores, car parking, landscaping, public open space,  a bus driver facility, highways works and infrastructure works. This application is accompanied by an Environmental Statement. (AMENDED PLANS / DOCUMENTS - FOR FURTHER DETAILS PLEASE REFER TO THE COVER LETTER ONLINE DATED 23 SEPTEMBER 2024). (Summary).
